race.comment: MARQUEE PLAYER (1) ran good time (27.74) when third last start over 484m at this track, the second placing in a row. Can make amends this time. SWEETEST SMILE (4) turned in a solid run last start over 457m at Q Lakeside finishing 4th and beaten only 3.5 lengths (25.69). Returns to a course where she has performed well. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Key player if finds best. WESTERN LIES (2) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Kingsbrae Wendy (23.99) in a Grade 3/4. Has the pace to be prominent. Will give a great sight again. MCKEON (7) placed last time out so worth considering.
